ogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-7088061744296615\";\n\t\t/* CrawlWiki skyscraper */\n\t\tgoogle_ad_slot = \"8196155564\";\n\t\tgoogle_ad_width = 160;\n\t\tgoogle_ad_height = 600;\n-->\n</script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</div>\n\n\t\t\t<a id=\"top\"></a>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"mw-indicators mw-body-content\">\n</div>\n\t\t\t<h1 id=\"firstHeading\" class=\"firstHeading\" lang=\"en\">Crystal Bolt</h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"bodyContent\" class=\"mw-body-content\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"siteSub\" class=\"noprint\">From CrawlWiki</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"contentSub\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"jump-to-nav\" class=\"mw-jump\">\n\t\t\t\t\tJump to:\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#mw-head\">navigation</a>, \t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#p-search\">search</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"mw-content-text\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\" class=\"mw-content-ltr\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div style=\"border: 1px solid #f00; background-color: #fcc; border-left: 15px solid #f00; margin-bottom: 20px; width: 100%; padding: 4px 10px; line-height: 1.1em; width: auto;\"><i><b>Obsolete</b>: This article refers to an aspect of the game which has been removed. It is retained for historical reference only.</i></div>\n<table style=\"background:#f5faff; border:1px solid #cedff2; width:auto; margin: 0px 5%; margin-bottom:1.25em; font-style:italic; text-align:left; color:#000; padding:1.5em 1em;\">\n\n<tr>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 100%;\"> Projects a penetrating projectile with peculiar magical properties. It is randomly imbued with either fire or ice, and additionally will reflect from walls of any material due to the crystal embedded in the shot.\n</td></tr></table>\n<p><b>Crystal Bolt</b> is a monster-only spell which launches an unusually reflectable bolt of <a href=\"/Fire\" title=\"Fire\">fire</a> or <a href=\"/Cold\" title=\"Cold\">cold</a> damage (50% chance of each). This bolt will bounce off of any surface, making <a href=\"/Multizap\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Multizap\">multizaps</a> a significant risk.\n</p><p>The following enemies cast Crystal Bolt:\n</p>\n<ul><li><span class=\"nhsym clr-green\">r</span> <a href=\"/File:Crystal_echidna.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Crystal echidna.png\" src=\"/images/0/05/Crystal_echidna.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/Crystal_echidna\" title=\"Crystal echidna\">Crystal echidna</a></b></li>\n<li><span class=\"nhsym clr-green\">9</span> <a href=\"/File:Crystal_guardian.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Crystal guardian.png\" src=\"/images/6/60/Crystal_guardian.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/Crystal_guardian\" title=\"Crystal guardian\">Crystal guardian</a></b></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Crystal Bolt was removed in <a href=\"/0.32\" title=\"0.32\">0.32</a>, replaced by <a href=\"/Crystallizing_Shot\" title=\"Crystallizing Shot\">Crystallizing Shot</a>.</li>\n<li>Crystal Bolt was added in <a href=\"/0.14\" title=\"0.14\">0.14</a>.</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20240916004141\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\n[SMW] In‐text annotation parser time: 0.001 seconds\nCPU time usage: 0.084 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.194 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 49/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 166/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 1109/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 338/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 5/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nLua time usage: 0.040s\nLua virtual size: 12.14 MB / 50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  153.653      1 -total\n 98.10%  150.732      2 Template:Monsterlink\n 96.85%  148.809      2 Template:Glyph\n  0.76%    1.161      1 Template:Obsolete\n  0.74%    1.130      1 Template:Flavour\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Save